12:53.125 --> 12:55.083
THEY'RE GOING FOR
THE BRASS RING UP THERE.

12:55.083 --> 12:57.625
I DID THAT,
SHOWED THEM THE WAY--

12:57.625 --> 12:59.208
LIKE A HEADLAMP
IN A COAL MINE.

12:59.208 --> 13:02.041
YOU SEE, FRANK GALLAGHER
KNOWS PEOPLE.

13:02.041 --> 13:04.208
I-I JUST INTUIT.

13:04.208 --> 13:08.168
I WAS, UH--I WAS
A PSYCHOLOGY MAJOR

13:08.168 --> 13:10.250
FOR A SEMESTER.

13:10.250 --> 13:11.542
- DAD?
- YEAH?

13:11.542 --> 13:13.542
- WHAT'S THIS?

13:13.542 --> 13:16.667
- UH, THAT'S A PACIFIER
FOR YOUR ANUS.

13:16.667 --> 13:19.125
[knock at door]

13:24.250 --> 13:26.375
- [panting]

13:26.375 --> 13:29.083
THEY'RE EARLY, FRANK!

13:29.083 --> 13:30.375
- HELLO.

13:30.375 --> 13:31.876
- CAN YOU BE ON BABY DUTY?

13:31.876 --> 13:34.250
- LOOKS LIKE A PRIEST
WITH A 'NAM VET.

13:34.250 --> 13:36.166
- HELLO?

13:36.166 --> 13:37.792
- IT'S F-FATHER PETE.

13:37.792 --> 13:40.041
HE'S WITH A HOSPICE PATIENT,
A NUN.

13:40.041 --> 13:43.126
THEY'RE OUT OF ROOM
AT ST. STEVEN'S.

13:43.126 --> 13:44.250
- [laughs]

13:44.250 --> 13:47.083
[baby crying]

13:47.083 --> 13:49.041
- HERE.
- OH, HYMIE.

13:49.041 --> 13:50.584
HEY.

13:50.584 --> 13:53.209
- HEY, NICE TO SEE YOU AGAIN,
FATHER PETE.

13:53.209 --> 13:56.168
- AND YOU TOO, JODY.

13:56.168 --> 13:57.709
- HI, I'M JODY.

13:57.709 --> 14:00.542
- [sighs]
I'M SORRY ABOUT THE MESS.

14:00.542 --> 14:03.250
WE'VE JUST BEEN
A LITTLE PREOCCUPIED.

14:03.250 --> 14:04.917
- NOT AT ALL.

14:04.917 --> 14:06.417
CAREFUL, CAREFUL.

14:06.417 --> 14:09.417
SHE'S NOT LONG FOR THIS WORLD,
I'M AFRAID.

14:09.417 --> 14:11.126
- OH.
- SHE'S TAKEN A VOW OF SILENCE,

14:11.126 --> 14:13.168
SO YOU DON'T HAVE TO WORRY
ABOUT HER

14:13.168 --> 14:15.084
KEEPING YOU UP ALL NIGHT
WITH HER PRAYING.

14:15.084 --> 14:16.625
- OH.

14:16.625 --> 14:18.917
- THIS IS HER
PAIN MEDICATION.

14:18.917 --> 14:20.333
- GREAT, YEAH.
- AND--AND--

14:20.333 --> 14:23.709
OH, AND MAKE SURE
HER IPAD IS ALWAYS CHARGED.

14:23.709 --> 14:27.042
SHE CAN PLAY ANGRY BIRDS
TILL THE COWS COME HOME.

14:27.042 --> 14:28.917
- OH, WELL--

14:28.917 --> 14:31.250
THAT'S JUST A, UM,
HARNESS FOR PATIENTS.

14:31.250 --> 14:34.292
- UH-HUH.
- UH, SHED KEY?

14:34.292 --> 14:37.001
- ON THE FRIDGE,
TOP OF THE FRIDGE.

14:37.001 --> 14:39.709
WHY ARE YOU ORANGE?

14:39.709 --> 14:41.125
FRANK?

14:41.125 --> 14:42.250
[baby crying]

14:42.250 --> 14:43.876
[door opens]

14:46.709 --> 14:48.041
- I DON'T KNOW
WHAT IT IS, RED,

14:48.041 --> 14:50.584
BUT, UH, I FEEL LESS ALONE
IN THE WORLD

14:50.584 --> 14:52.083
KNOWING I CAN
DRIVE ACROSS TOWN

14:52.083 --> 14:58.209
AND FIND YOU HERE,
BENT OVER CANS OF CHICKEN STOCK.

15:00.750 --> 15:03.250
[sighs]
LOOK. I-I'M SORRY.

15:03.250 --> 15:07.083
TRULY. I JUST--

15:07.083 --> 15:09.041
[sighs]

15:09.041 --> 15:12.125
CAN YOU FORGIVE A MAN
WHO'S FALLING APART?

15:12.125 --> 15:14.333
A LITTLE?

15:16.750 --> 15:18.126
- YEAH.

15:18.126 --> 15:20.333
[door opens]

15:20.333 --> 15:22.625
- CAN I KISS YOU?
- NO.

15:22.625 --> 15:23.917
- JUST A LITTLE.

15:27.000 --> 15:29.542
SO LISTEN.

15:29.542 --> 15:33.084
UM, I NEED SOMEBODY
TO ROB MY HOUSE,

15:33.084 --> 15:35.250
AND I'M HOPING
YOU COULD HELP.

15:35.250 --> 15:38.084
- YOU WANT ME
TO ROB YOUR HOUSE?

15:38.084 --> 15:39.792
- CANDACE CHANGED THE LOCKS
ON THE HOUSE--

15:39.792 --> 15:41.667
MY GODDAMN HOUSE.

15:41.667 --> 15:43.084
AND SHE WON'T LET ME
BACK IN,

15:43.084 --> 15:46.084
SO I NEED SOMEONE
TO STEAL MY STUFF.

15:46.084 --> 15:49.084
IF I DO IT, THE NEIGHBORS
MIGHT RECOGNIZE ME.

15:50.750 --> 15:52.792
YOU GO IN DURING
DAYLIGHT HOURS

15:52.792 --> 15:54.250
AND YOU LOOK LIKE MOVERS.

15:54.250 --> 15:57.083
YOU'LL BE FINE.

15:57.083 --> 15:59.166
LOOK, SHE STAYS UP
TILL 3:00 A.M.

15:59.166 --> 16:01.584
DRINKING STOLI VANILLA
AND WATCHING BOWFLEX ADS.

16:01.584 --> 16:05.084
SHE'LL BE UNCONSCIOUS
UNTIL WELL PAST NOON.

16:07.500 --> 16:09.834
OKAY, THIS COULD BE
VERY LUCRATIVE FOR YOU.

16:09.834 --> 16:11.168
YOU CAN TAKE ANYTHING
YOU WANT.

16:11.168 --> 16:12.208
COME ON,
IT'S ALL INSURED.

16:12.208 --> 16:15.083
ALL I WANT
ARE MY TWO ARMANI SUITS,

16:15.083 --> 16:17.126
MY LUCIEN FREUD,
AND MY BOTTLE

16:17.126 --> 16:21.000
OF 1990 CHATEAU LATOUR
PAUILLAC.

16:21.000 --> 16:22.458
WHAT DO YOU SAY?

16:22.458 --> 16:25.042
WILL YOU DO IT?

16:29.041 --> 16:31.083
- FRANK?
- YES, SON?

16:31.083 --> 16:33.042
- WHY WOULD A DUDE
PUT HIS PENIS

16:33.042 --> 16:34.834
IN ANOTHER DUDE'S MOUTH?

16:34.834 --> 16:38.333
- WELL, SOMETIMES MEN DISCOVER
THINGS ABOUT THEMSELVES,

16:38.333 --> 16:40.834
LIKE THEY PREFER
MALE GENITALIA

16:40.834 --> 16:42.166
TO FEMALE GENITALIA.

16:42.166 --> 16:43.876
- WAIT.

16:43.876 --> 16:46.166
SO SOME GUYS
LIKE TO LICK WIENERS?

16:46.166 --> 16:48.792
- WELL, I'M SURE
AT FIRST THEY'RE ATTRACTED

16:48.792 --> 16:50.333
TO EACH OTHER'S BUILD.

16:50.333 --> 16:52.333
AND ONCE A CONNECTION
GETS MADE,

16:52.333 --> 16:54.750
THEN THE WIENERS
GET LICKED.

16:54.750 --> 16:57.750
IT'S A SCORCHER TODAY,
AIN'T IT?

17:04.292 --> 17:06.417
- HEY, DEBS,
HOW WAS THE POOL?

17:06.417 --> 17:08.417
- GREAT.
WHERE ARE THE SWIM DIAPERS?

17:08.417 --> 17:12.584
- THANKS. UH, AISLE NINE.

17:12.584 --> 17:15.126
AAH!

17:15.126 --> 17:17.625
DID YOU PUT TACKS
IN MY DRAWER?

17:17.625 --> 17:20.667
- MY BABY SISTER
SHOULDA GOT YOUR JOB.

17:20.667 --> 17:22.000
IT TOOK MY FOUR MONTHS
TO TEACH HER

17:22.000 --> 17:24.292
HOW TO SWALLOW WITHOUT GAGGING,
AND FOR WHAT?

17:24.292 --> 17:26.709
YEAH, IT'S NOT HER FAULT
SHE GOT A LAZY EYE.

17:26.709 --> 17:28.417
SHE WAS RAISED RIGHT.

17:28.417 --> 17:30.542
SHE DON'T THINK
SHE'S BETTER THAN NOBODY.

17:30.542 --> 17:32.458
- I'M SORRY
ABOUT YOUR SISTER,

17:32.458 --> 17:35.084
BUT I GOT
FIVE KIDS TO FEED.

17:38.750 --> 17:40.667
- FIONA?

17:40.667 --> 17:44.959
- OH, YOU KNOW,
JUST EMPLOYEE SHENANIGANS.

17:44.959 --> 17:47.959
YOU GOT COUPONS FOR THIS?

17:50.542 --> 17:54.250
- I'VE GOT AN 11:00
OVARIAN CYST, AN 11:30 U.T.I.,

17:54.250 --> 17:55.750
AND A PRETEEN
PREGNANCY IN THE LOBBY.

17:55.750 --> 17:57.126
SO CAN YOU TELL ME
WHY YOU'RE HERE

17:57.126 --> 17:58.458
WHEN I JUST SAW YOU
TWO WEEKS AGO?

17:58.458 --> 18:00.209
- WE'VE BEEN BANGIN'
LIKE BUNNIES

18:00.209 --> 18:01.500
AND I CAN'T GET PREGNANT.
I NEED ANOTHER EXAM.

18:01.500 --> 18:02.876
- IT WON'T CHANGE ANYTHING.

18:02.876 --> 18:04.166
- BUT YOU SAID LAST TIME
I HAD A CHANCE

18:04.166 --> 18:05.834
OF GETTING PREGNANT.

18:05.834 --> 18:07.292
- I BELIEVE I SAID
YOU HAD VERY LITTLE CHANCE.

18:07.292 --> 18:09.041
I ALSO USED THE WORDS,
"HIGHLY UNLIKELY"

18:09.041 --> 18:10.792
AND "WILDLY IMPROBABLE."

18:10.792 --> 18:13.375
- YOU GOT MY BABY GIRL'S
HOPES UP FOR NOTHING.

18:13.375 --> 18:15.417
- I CHOSE TO MITIGATE
A DIFFICULT DISCUSSION

18:15.417 --> 18:17.166
WITH UPBEAT
AND POSITIVE PHRASINGS.

18:17.166 --> 18:18.375
- I NEED TO KNOW
THE TRUTH.

18:18.375 --> 18:19.917
CAN I HAVE A DAMN BABY
OR NOT?

18:19.917 --> 18:23.667
- PUT IS THIS WAY,
YOU HAVE A 99.999 CHANCE

18:23.667 --> 18:27.084
OF NOT GETTING PREGNANT,
NOTHING IS IMPOSSIBLE.

18:33.042 --> 18:35.417
- SO DOES, LIKE, ONE PENIS
GO INTO THE OTHER PENIS?

18:35.417 --> 18:37.000
- OF COURSE.
WHEN GAY DUDES GET HORNY,

18:37.000 --> 18:39.168
THEIR PEE HOLES OPEN.

18:40.250 --> 18:42.709
[jackhammering]

18:42.709 --> 18:44.168
- HEY.

18:44.168 --> 18:46.125
SWIM DIAPERS.
- THANK GOD.

18:46.125 --> 18:48.417
I'VE ALREADY HAD
TO FISH OUT TWO POOPS.

18:48.417 --> 18:50.959
EW.

18:50.959 --> 18:53.000
[jackhammering]

18:53.000 --> 18:56.084
[electric buzzing]

18:58.792 --> 19:00.041
[sparks]

19:00.041 --> 19:01.417
- DADDY!

19:01.417 --> 19:02.876
- HEY. WHOA.

19:02.876 --> 19:04.041
YOU STINK LIKE BLEACH.

19:04.041 --> 19:06.042
- YEAH, I WAS
AT THE POOL TODAY.

19:06.042 --> 19:07.584
I STAYED UNDER
FOR 112 SECONDS.

19:07.584 --> 19:09.667
- HEY, GOOD FOR YOU!
- YEAH.

19:09.667 --> 19:12.458
- SHOW THOSE SYPHILIS-RIDDEN
TURBO SLUTS A THING OR TWO.

19:12.458 --> 19:13.709
THEY THINK
THEY OWN THE WATER

19:13.709 --> 19:15.876
JUST 'CAUSE
THEY PISS IN IT.

19:15.876 --> 19:17.709
[clank]
- WE HIT SOMETHING.

19:17.709 --> 19:19.250
- WHAT'S THAT SMELL?

19:19.250 --> 19:21.417
- EW.
- WHEW.

19:21.417 --> 19:23.584
- THE SEWER LINE?
- OH, MAN.

19:23.584 --> 19:26.166
YOU PROBABLY SHOULD
PATCH THAT UP

19:26.166 --> 19:27.917
WITH SOME DUCT TAPE
AND A T-SHIRT.

19:27.917 --> 19:30.126
AAH, GOD. BLEH.

19:30.126 --> 19:33.126
[rock music]

19:33.126 --> 19:34.500
♪ ♪

19:34.500 --> 19:37.333
- YOU SURE WE'RE DIGGING
IN THE RIGHT SPOT?

19:37.333 --> 19:38.625
- EW!
- [coughs]

19:38.625 --> 19:40.125
- AAH!

19:40.125 --> 19:48.126
♪ ♪

19:48.126 --> 19:49.834
- MAN, I CAN'T BELIEVE
YOUR WIFE

19:49.834 --> 19:51.417
ACTUALLY CAME TO YOUR HOUSE.

19:51.417 --> 19:54.458
- I THOUGHT V WAS GONNA
RIP HER THROAT OUT.

19:54.458 --> 19:56.250
YO, SO WHAT'S UP
WITH YOU AND MANDY?

19:56.250 --> 19:57.834
YOU GUYS SEEM TIGHT.

19:57.834 --> 19:59.458
- I GUESS.

19:59.458 --> 20:01.041
SHE'S GOTTEN HELLA CLINGY.

20:01.041 --> 20:04.126
- YOU RESCUED
HER CROSS-DRESSING SIBLING.

20:04.126 --> 20:06.500
YOU SWASHBUCKLED
THAT SHIT, MAN.

20:06.500 --> 20:08.083
SEALS THE DEAL FOR A CHICK,
I'M SERIOUS.

20:08.083 --> 20:11.001
GIRLS TAKE THAT HERO CRAP
STRAIGHT TO THE BANK.

20:11.001 --> 20:12.917
SHE COOK FOR YOU NOW?

20:12.917 --> 20:15.292
FOLD YOUR CLOTHES?
- SOMETIMES.

20:15.292 --> 20:18.083
- SHE STAY OVER
MORE THAN FOUR NIGHTS A WEEK?

20:18.083 --> 20:20.209
HELP YOU OUT
WITH RANDOM STUFF?

20:20.209 --> 20:22.792
HUH?
[laughs]

20:22.792 --> 20:25.750
DUDE,
YOU ARE GHETTO MARRIED.

20:25.750 --> 20:27.750
ENJOY IT.
YOU GET ALL THE PERKS,

20:27.750 --> 20:29.250
NO PAPERWORK.

20:29.250 --> 20:31.917
GUYS WOULD KILL
FOR THAT SETUP.

20:31.917 --> 20:34.084
- I KINDA HATE IT.

20:34.084 --> 20:35.625
- WHAT'S WRONG WITH YOU, MAN?

20:35.625 --> 20:38.625
I THINK KAREN
MESSED YOU UP BAD.

20:43.042 --> 20:45.292
- GUN IT.

20:45.292 --> 20:49.168
♪ ♪

20:49.168 --> 20:53.292
- AH, GOOD WORK.

20:58.417 --> 21:00.959
[knock at door]

21:00.959 --> 21:02.959
[baby crying]

21:02.959 --> 21:05.168
- GET YOUR ACT TOGETHER,
LADY.

21:05.168 --> 21:06.458
- [sighs]

21:06.458 --> 21:10.083
I GOT DAY-OLD CHUCK,
TWO-DAY-OLD SIRLOIN,

21:10.083 --> 21:12.500
COUPLE OF
PARTIALLY SOFT BAGELS,

21:12.500 --> 21:15.667
AND, LIKE, TWO GALLONS
OF NEARLY EXPIRED MAYO.

21:15.667 --> 21:17.333
OH, AND A SHEET CAKE.

21:17.333 --> 21:19.542
- JOANIE WAS LATE
PICKING UP HER KID AGAIN.

21:19.542 --> 21:21.084
AND GUESS WHAT THE EXCUSE WAS.

21:21.084 --> 21:22.500
- FLAT TIRE?
- FLAT TIRE.

21:22.500 --> 21:23.917
- IT'S NOT THE HOMO THING
THAT GETS ME,

21:23.917 --> 21:25.041
'CAUSE GAYS HIT ON ME
ALL THE TIME

21:25.041 --> 21:26.166
AND IT DOESN'T BOTHER ME.

21:26.166 --> 21:27.292
- OF COURSE THEY DO.

21:27.292 --> 21:28.375
YOU WEAR DESIGNER JEANS

21:28.375 --> 21:29.876
AND COCONUT HAIR PRODUCT.

21:29.876 --> 21:31.083
YOU'RE LIKE GAY FLYPAPER.

21:31.083 --> 21:33.250
"HADDY BIRTHDAY JUBY?"

21:33.250 --> 21:35.041
- BAKERY GUY IS DYSLEXIC.

21:35.041 --> 21:36.750
WHERE'S FRANK?
- HAVEN'T SEEN HIM.

21:36.750 --> 21:38.292
- WELL, HE'S GOTTA
FILL IN THAT HOLE

21:38.292 --> 21:39.917
WHERE GINGER WAS,
IT REEKS OUT THERE.

21:39.917 --> 21:41.083
- HE FORGOT
WHERE HE BURIED HER.

21:41.083 --> 21:42.750
- YOU'RE KIDDING.

21:42.750 --> 21:44.500
- WE COULDN'T FIND HER.

21:44.500 --> 21:46.959
- AND CARL BUSTED
THE SEWER LINE.

21:46.959 --> 21:48.750
- WAIT.
YOU PICKING UP GUITAR?

21:48.750 --> 21:50.709
- BITCHES AT WORK
GIVING ME SHIT.

21:50.709 --> 21:52.126
THUMB TACKS
IN MY CHANGE DRAWER.

21:52.126 --> 21:53.166
YOU BELIEVE THAT?

21:53.166 --> 21:54.500
- HOLY SHIT.

21:54.500 --> 21:57.083
- YEP. YEAH, WE DID GOOD.

21:57.083 --> 21:58.834
BOOMTOWN WAS GOOD TO US.
- YEAH.

21:58.834 --> 22:00.750
- BLOWING UP
THE HANCOCK BUILDING?

22:00.750 --> 22:02.126
- NO, WE DON'T HAVE
ANY MORE ROOM IN THE TRUCK.

22:02.126 --> 22:03.750
CAN WE STORE SOME HERE?
- ARE YOU NUTS?

22:03.750 --> 22:05.125
LOOK AT THAT KID'S FACE.

22:05.125 --> 22:07.417
- I PROMISE I'LL PUT IT
IN A NO-CARL ZONE.

22:07.417 --> 22:09.126
- AS IF THAT EXISTS.

22:09.126 --> 22:11.084
- DON'T TOUCH IT.
- GO WASH YOUR FACE, PYRO.

22:11.084 --> 22:12.876
MANDY, MAKE YOURSELF USEFUL.
SET THE TABLE.

22:12.876 --> 22:14.542
- YOU WANT POP, BEER,
OR ICE WATER?

22:14.542 --> 22:16.333
- UH, WATER'S GOOD.
THANKS.

22:16.333 --> 22:18.125
- PUT THESE
ON LIP'S BED.

22:22.001 --> 22:24.542
- SHE'S OUT IN A WEEK, OKAY?
- WHICH ONE?

22:26.001 --> 22:27.333
- [sighs]

22:27.333 --> 22:28.709
- WHAT'S WITH JIMMY?

22:28.709 --> 22:30.375
THAT SHIT WITH HIS DAD?

22:30.375 --> 22:31.959
- HE'S PRETTY BROKEN UP
ABOUT IT.

22:31.959 --> 22:34.166
- NO ONE'S DEAD, WOUNDED,
OR INCARCERATED.

22:34.166 --> 22:37.126
- WHAT DO YOU EXPECT?
RICH KID FROM THE NORTH SIDE--

22:37.126 --> 22:38.375
- IT'S HIS FIRST
BIG FAMILY CRISIS.

22:38.375 --> 22:39.917
HE'S TAKING IT
PRETTY HARD.

22:39.917 --> 22:42.168
LEFT SIDE OF YOUR MOUTH.

22:42.168 --> 22:43.959
OTHER LEFT.
- DUDE'S GOT DADDY ISSUES.

22:43.959 --> 22:46.250
NO WONDER YOU DIG HIM.
- I CAN HEAR YOU.

22:46.250 --> 22:48.168
- HEY, LIP, GO REORGANIZE
THE TRUCK.

22:48.168 --> 22:50.584
PUT THE WEED IN THE FRIDGE,
POPPERS IN THE FREEZER.

22:50.584 --> 22:52.125
PUT THE SMOKES ON TOP
AND THE BANGERS

22:52.125 --> 22:53.750
UNDERNEATH THE SEATS.
- YEP.

22:53.750 --> 22:55.001
- I'LL HELP.

22:55.001 --> 22:56.166
- CAKE FOR DINNER?

22:56.166 --> 22:57.709
- I GOTTA
GET TO THE ALIBI.

22:57.709 --> 22:59.584
HEY, WHAT DID THE DOC
SAY THIS MORNING?

22:59.584 --> 23:02.126
- NEVER HAD A CHANCE TO GO.

23:02.126 --> 23:04.208
- OKAY. I LOVE YOU.
MWAH.

23:08.834 --> 23:10.208
[door shuts]

23:15.208 --> 23:17.292
- HEY.

23:17.292 --> 23:18.876
WHAT ABOUT A SURROGATE?

23:18.876 --> 23:21.084
- YOU OFFERING?
- HELL NO.

23:21.084 --> 23:23.209
BET YOU COULD FIND SOMEONE GOOD
ON CRAIGSLIST.

23:23.209 --> 23:25.542
- BITCH GETS PAID,
I.V.F. DOCS GETS PAID,

23:25.542 --> 23:27.041
MEDICAL BILLS,
MATERNITY CLOTHES,

23:27.041 --> 23:28.584
LAWYER FEE, CONTRACT FEES.

23:28.584 --> 23:30.084
LOW END? 40 GRAND.

23:30.084 --> 23:31.250
NEED A TRUCKLOAD
OF SLAVE-PLAY

23:31.250 --> 23:33.250
TO RAISE THAT KINDA SCRATCH.

23:33.250 --> 23:34.959
- WHAT'LL YOU DO?

23:34.959 --> 23:37.166
- SOMETHING.

23:37.166 --> 23:41.041
- SISTER, I SO ADMIRE
THE VOW YOU'VE TAKEN.

23:41.041 --> 23:43.333
IT TAKES SUCH STRENGTH

23:43.333 --> 23:46.168
TO RESIST THE LURE
OF TEMPTATION,

23:46.168 --> 23:50.333
VERBALLY OR OTHERWISE.

23:51.500 --> 23:53.542
[clatter upstairs]
OH!

23:53.542 --> 23:56.542
OH, SISTER, I'M--
I'M SO SORRY.

23:56.542 --> 23:58.959
JODY AND I ARE JUST
EXPERIMENTING

23:58.959 --> 24:01.625
WITH NEW LIBERTIES.

24:01.625 --> 24:04.041
[drill whirring]

24:04.041 --> 24:08.250
AS YOU KNOW, OUR BODIES
ARE GOD'S TEMPLE,

24:08.250 --> 24:12.168
AND IT'S AS IF WE'RE ADDING ON
A LITTLE WING OR TWO.

24:15.126 --> 24:18.208
SO THERE'S NO WAY
IN THE WORLD

24:18.208 --> 24:20.208
YOU WOULD EVER TALK?

24:20.208 --> 24:22.250
[drilling]

24:24.625 --> 24:27.959
[sighs]
OH, SISTER.

24:27.959 --> 24:31.083
JODY IS PUSHING ME
TO NEW LEVELS.

24:31.083 --> 24:33.250
IT'S COMPLETELY MY FAULT.

24:33.250 --> 24:35.209
HE WARNED ME NOT TO GO

24:35.209 --> 24:38.250
THROUGH THIS GATEWAY
WITH HIM,

24:38.250 --> 24:39.917
BUT I WOULDN'T LISTEN.

24:39.917 --> 24:42.126
AND NOW I CAN'T
FIND MY WAY BACK.

24:42.126 --> 24:44.292
[crying] I'VE NEVER HAD
SO MANY THINGS

24:44.292 --> 24:50.166
INSERTED INTO SO MANY
PARTS OF MY BODY AT ONCE!

24:50.166 --> 24:55.209
HAVE I ENCOURAGED HIM
TO OVERSTEP HIS BOUNDARIES?

24:55.209 --> 24:57.292
OR AM I HELPING HIM
TO CREATE

24:57.292 --> 25:00.041
NEW AND--AND HEALTHY ONES?

25:04.250 --> 25:07.000
BECAUSE I ADMIT,

25:07.000 --> 25:11.083
INFLICTING SEXUAL PAIN

25:11.083 --> 25:14.959
GIVES ME
GREAT PLEASURE.

25:17.168 --> 25:20.333
- YOU READY, MAMA?
BATTERIES ARE CHARGED!

25:20.333 --> 25:22.542
- OH, SISTER,
I FEEL SO MUCH BETTER.

25:22.542 --> 25:27.542
THANK YOU FOR LETTING ME
GET THAT OFF MY CHEST.

25:27.542 --> 25:29.834
OH, YOU'RE A GOOD ONE.

25:33.709 --> 25:35.792
- GLOVES?

25:35.792 --> 25:38.792
- GOT SOME CUTS
ON MY HANDS AT WORK.

25:40.250 --> 25:42.876
I THINK IT'S DRY.
- OH, SORRY.

25:42.876 --> 25:44.584
OH, MY GOD.

25:44.584 --> 25:46.168
I JUST REALIZED.

25:46.168 --> 25:48.166
THAT HUGE FIGHT
THAT DAD HAD WITH MR. WARD,

25:48.166 --> 25:49.709
MY GAY SEVENTH GRADE
SCIENCE TEACHER--

25:49.709 --> 25:50.876
I THOUGHT IT WAS BECAUSE
OF THE CRAPPY GRADE

25:50.876 --> 25:52.209
I GOT ON
MY BREAD MOLD PROJECT,

25:52.209 --> 25:53.250
BUT THEY KEPT ON
EXCUSING THEMSELVES

25:53.250 --> 25:54.584
TO DISCUSS IT IN PRIVATE.

25:54.584 --> 25:56.458
I AM SUCH AN IDIOT.

25:56.458 --> 25:58.166
AND THAT WEDDING
THAT WE WENT TO IN HAWAII

25:58.166 --> 26:00.001
WHEN I WAS IN HIGH SCHOOL--
ME, MOM, AND CHIP

26:00.001 --> 26:01.250
WENT TO BED EARLY
AND DAD STAYED UP DANCING

26:01.250 --> 26:03.792
ALL NIGHT
WITH THE BEST MAN.

26:03.792 --> 26:05.083
I GUESS WHAT
REALLY GETS ME

26:05.083 --> 26:06.834
IS THAT HE COULDN'T
TELL ME THE TRUTH.

26:06.834 --> 26:08.084
I MEAN, DID HE THINK
I WOULDN'T ACCEPT HIM

26:08.084 --> 26:09.208
OR THAT
I'D THINK LESS OF HIM?

26:09.208 --> 26:11.126
WHY DIDN'T HE TRUST ME?

26:11.126 --> 26:12.333
AM I THE ONLY ONE
WHO DIDN'T KNOW?

26:12.333 --> 26:13.917
DOES MY BROTHER KNOW?

26:13.917 --> 26:15.292
OH, I BET YOU
MY BROTHER KNOWS.

26:15.292 --> 26:18.292
[Take Me Out to the Coast
by Waters]

26:18.292 --> 26:22.876
♪ ♪

26:22.876 --> 26:25.084
- ♪ AND I WAS WRONG ♪

26:25.084 --> 26:29.876
♪ TO BELIEVE IN MYSELF ♪

26:29.876 --> 26:32.834
♪ I CAN'T BELONG
TO A SCENE ♪

26:32.834 --> 26:34.417
♪ AND NO ONE ELSE ♪

26:34.417 --> 26:36.667
- WAIT, SO THERE'S
BUTTHOLE INVOLVED?

26:36.667 --> 26:39.959
- SOMETIMES, NOT ALWAYS.

26:39.959 --> 26:41.292
HEY. IAN AND I ARE GONNA
GO GET HIGH

26:41.292 --> 26:43.126
AND WATCH FAMILY GUY.
YOU WANNA COME?

26:43.126 --> 26:44.500
- UH, NO, I'VE BEEN
DRIVING ALL DAY.

26:44.500 --> 26:45.959
I'M EXHAUSTED.

26:45.959 --> 26:47.126
- DOING A NIGHT LOAD.

26:47.126 --> 26:50.292
ANY TAKERS?

26:50.292 --> 26:51.458
- HERE YOU GO.

26:51.458 --> 26:53.126
- LIP, NOTHING?

26:53.126 --> 26:54.667
- DID OURS
THIS AFTERNOON.

26:54.667 --> 26:56.375
- MAYBE NEXT TIME
YOU WANNA THROW IN

26:56.375 --> 26:59.084
DEBBIE OR CARL OR LIAM'S
WITH YOURS.

26:59.084 --> 27:02.000
- SURE, NO PROBLEM.

27:02.000 --> 27:03.876
HEY, IF YOU
CHANGE YOUR MIND,

27:03.876 --> 27:05.375
COME DOWN, OKAY?

27:05.375 --> 27:07.375
- MWAH.

27:10.625 --> 27:14.084
- I NEED TO KNOW
WHERE THE GAY WIENERS GO.

27:14.084 --> 27:16.959
- [sighs]

27:16.959 --> 27:19.250
YOU KNOW HOW YOU PLUNGE
A TOILET WHEN IT'S BACKED UP?

27:19.250 --> 27:20.500
- YEAH.

27:20.500 --> 27:22.125
- THINK OF IT AS
ONE DUDE

27:22.125 --> 27:24.168
PLUNGING ANOTHER DUDE'S
TOILET.

27:24.168 --> 27:27.168
♪ ♪

27:27.168 --> 27:30.250
- ♪ TAKE US OUT
TO THE COAST ♪

27:30.250 --> 27:36.042
♪ AND WE'LL FIND
OUR WAY, OH ♪

27:36.042 --> 27:37.333
- COULD ALWAYS ADOPT.

27:37.333 --> 27:38.917
- I DON'T WANT
SOMEONE ELSE'S KID.

27:38.917 --> 27:40.333
I WANT A LITTLE PUNK
WITH YOUR PRETTY EYES

27:40.333 --> 27:44.208
AND YOUR CROOKED SMILE.

27:44.208 --> 27:45.959
- I DON'T KNOW, V,
AT SOME POINT

27:45.959 --> 27:50.250
WE MIGHT HAVE TO ACCEPT
THAT IT'S NOT MEANT TO BE.

27:50.250 --> 27:53.584
- NOT MEANT TO BE?

27:53.584 --> 27:55.792
WAS I MEANT TO GET
AN S.T.D. AT 17

27:55.792 --> 27:57.250
FROM SOME LAME-ASS RAPPER

27:57.250 --> 27:59.250
THAT WOULD
TRASH MY TUBES?

27:59.250 --> 28:00.959
WAS I MEANT TO GOOGLE HIM
ALL AFTERNOON

28:00.959 --> 28:02.834
TO FIND OUT
HE HAS EIGHT KIDS?

28:02.834 --> 28:04.667
WAS I MEANT TO FRIEND HIM
ON FACEBOOK

28:04.667 --> 28:06.709
TO WRITE ON HIS WALL
SOME PSYCHOTIC RANT

28:06.709 --> 28:08.166
ABOUT HOW
HE RUINED MY LIFE?

28:08.166 --> 28:10.292
- BABY, IT'S OKAY.
- NO, IT'S NOT.

28:10.292 --> 28:11.834
FUCK HIS WEAK-ASS RHYMES,

28:11.834 --> 28:13.584
FUCK THAT
TREE FROG-LOOKIN' DOCTOR,

28:13.584 --> 28:15.584
AND FUCK ALL THE FUCKIN' MONEY
I SPENT ON CONDOMS

28:15.584 --> 28:17.041
FOR THE LAST 20 YEARS.

28:17.041 --> 28:18.375
AND FUCK YOU FOR ACTING LIKE
YOU DON'T WANNA

28:18.375 --> 28:22.041
FIGHT HARDER FOR THIS.
- WHOA.

28:22.041 --> 28:26.000
YOU KNOW I DO,
MORE THAN ANYTHING.

28:26.000 --> 28:29.834
- THEN LET'S FIGHT.

28:29.834 --> 28:32.084
[laughs]

28:40.834 --> 28:42.750
- ENOUGH WITH THE KICKING!

28:42.750 --> 28:45.041
CHRIST!
- WHERE IS SHE?

28:45.041 --> 28:47.625
- I CAN'T--
I GIVE UP.

28:47.625 --> 28:49.084
I NEED SLEEP.

28:49.084 --> 28:50.125
- LET ME SPELL THIS OUT
FOR YOU.

28:50.125 --> 28:51.667
THE CITY DIGS UP
SOME BONES.

28:51.667 --> 28:53.042
THE POLICE SHOW UP.

28:53.042 --> 28:55.042
THEY FIGURE OUT
IT'S AUNT GINGER.

28:55.042 --> 28:56.584
THEY DATE THE BONES.

28:56.584 --> 28:58.542
THEY REALIZE SHE'S BEEN DEAD
FOR 14 YEARS.

28:58.542 --> 29:00.917
AND YET,
HER SOCIAL SECURITY CHECKS

29:00.917 --> 29:03.375
ARE BEING CASHED
EVERY MONTH.

29:03.375 --> 29:05.834
THIS ISN'T A DUI, FRANK.

29:05.834 --> 29:08.126
YOU BURIED A BODY
AND YOU STOLE

29:08.126 --> 29:09.292
FROM THE FEDERAL GOVERNMENT.

29:09.292 --> 29:13.042
YOU WILL NEVER
GET OUT OF PRISON.

29:13.042 --> 29:15.375
THINK ABOUT IT.

29:18.458 --> 29:20.208
- FUCK.

29:20.208 --> 29:24.041
[gunshots]

29:25.500 --> 29:28.208
- HEY.
YOU KNOW THE GUY

29:28.208 --> 29:30.208
YOU BEAT THE SHIT OUT OF
AT THAT CLUB?

29:30.208 --> 29:32.333
HE WANTS ME TO SNEAK
INTO HIS MANSION,

29:32.333 --> 29:34.083
TAKE ALL OF HIS CRAP.

29:34.083 --> 29:35.750
- REALLY?

29:35.750 --> 29:37.458
HILARIOUS.
[gunshot]

29:37.458 --> 29:41.458
- HE CAN'T GET IT HIMSELF.
DIVORCE.

29:41.458 --> 29:42.709
SAYS I CAN TAKE
WHATEVER I WANT.

29:42.709 --> 29:44.125
HE'S LOADED.
YOU WANT IN?

29:44.125 --> 29:48.625
[gunshots]

29:48.625 --> 29:51.042
JESUS!
USE BLANKS, MAYBE?

29:51.042 --> 29:52.000
FUCK.

29:52.000 --> 29:53.667
- CAN I BRING MY COUSINS?

29:53.667 --> 29:55.208
- YEAH.
- ALL RIGHT.

29:55.208 --> 29:57.709
I'M IN.
[gunshot]

29:57.709 --> 29:59.126
I DON'T KNOW WHAT YOU SEE

29:59.126 --> 30:01.625
IN THAT GERIATRIC
VIAGROID.

30:01.625 --> 30:03.584
- HE BUYS ME STUFF,
ORDERS ME ROOM SERVICE.

30:03.584 --> 30:05.083
[gunshots]

30:08.166 --> 30:10.126
HE ISN'T AFRAID
TO KISS ME.

30:10.126 --> 30:14.001
[ice cream truck chimes]

30:16.584 --> 30:17.959
- YEAH, WE'RE LOW ON JOINTS.

30:17.959 --> 30:19.166
- I GOT EXTRA WEED
IN THE FRIDGE,

30:19.166 --> 30:20.709
BUT IT NEEDS ROLLING.

30:20.709 --> 30:23.001
- YOU GUYS LOOK LIKE
YOU COULD USE SOME HELP.

30:23.001 --> 30:26.083
- YEAH, THAT'D BE GREAT.
- NO, WE'RE GOOD, THANKS.

30:26.083 --> 30:27.166
- CAN YOU ROLL US
SOME SPLIFFS?

30:27.166 --> 30:29.041
- SURE.
WE NEED PAPERS.

30:29.041 --> 30:30.792
- RIGHT THERE.

30:30.792 --> 30:33.375
- YOU GUYS
ARE REALLY KILLING IT.

30:33.375 --> 30:35.166
- WHOA, YOU ARE A GIANT.

30:35.166 --> 30:37.542
- ASK ME IF I PLAY BASKETBALL
AND I'LL PUNCH YOUR NUTS.

30:37.542 --> 30:39.083
- WHAT DO YOU WANT?

30:39.083 --> 30:40.959
- TWO FOUNTAINS,
A PACK OF SPARKLERS,

30:40.959 --> 30:42.417
THREE JOINTS,
AND A BOMB POP.

30:42.417 --> 30:45.042
- HEY, YOU GOT ANY
COMMUNITY SERVICE HOURS LEFT?

30:45.042 --> 30:47.375
- WHY?
- MOLLY COULD HELP, HE OFFERED.

30:47.375 --> 30:49.042
- NO. YOU KNOW WHAT?
I'M COVERED.

30:49.042 --> 30:51.542
ACTUALLY WE'RE GOOD HERE TOO.
YOU CAN GO HOME.

30:51.542 --> 30:53.126
- YOU KNOW WHAT?
HAVE HER STICK AROUND.

30:53.126 --> 30:54.417
I GOTTA HIT THE ALIBI
IN TEN MINUTES AWAY.

30:54.417 --> 30:55.709
- I CAN HANDLE IT.
- I'M GOOD TO STAY.

30:55.709 --> 30:59.000
- NO, PLEASE JUST
GO HOME, MANDY--

30:59.000 --> 31:03.126
TO YOUR OWN FUCKING HOUSE,
FOR ONCE.

31:12.709 --> 31:15.375
- THAT WAS HARSH.

31:15.375 --> 31:18.041
[toilet flushes]

31:27.333 --> 31:29.917
- [exhales]

31:29.917 --> 31:31.333
- REALLY, LADIES?

31:31.333 --> 31:35.001
REALLY FUNNY.
[knocking]

31:37.209 --> 31:39.126
[phone line trilling]

31:39.126 --> 31:40.375
HI, THIS IS FIONA.

31:40.375 --> 31:42.168
I'M WORKING REGISTER TWO.

31:42.168 --> 31:43.959
I'M LOCKED IN THE BATHROOM.

31:43.959 --> 31:46.166
I DID TRY THE KNOB.

31:46.166 --> 31:49.000
FINE. I'LL TRY AGAIN.

31:55.292 --> 31:59.168
- ON WHAT PLANET
IS IT COOL FOR YOU

31:59.168 --> 32:01.126
TO TAKE A SMOKE BREAK
IN THE EMPLOYEE BATHROOM?

32:01.126 --> 32:03.000
- I DON'T EVEN
SMOKE PARLIAMENTS.

32:03.000 --> 32:05.750
[rock music]

32:05.750 --> 32:08.917
- ♪ I REMEMBER ♪

32:08.917 --> 32:12.458
♪ HOW I PLAYED
THE FOOL FOR YOU ♪

32:12.458 --> 32:17.458
♪ NOW I'M JUST A FOOL ♪

32:17.458 --> 32:23.001
♪ UNTIL YOU DO THIS EVERY TIME ♪

32:23.001 --> 32:25.792
♪ THAT I WAKE ♪

32:25.792 --> 32:31.084
♪ IS A NUMBER THAT SINGS ♪

32:31.084 --> 32:39.084
♪ ♪

32:40.750 --> 32:43.333
- HOLY CRAP,
CONGRATS ON YOUR PUBERTY.

32:43.333 --> 32:46.250
- YEAH, YOUR TITS
LOOK GREAT.

32:46.250 --> 32:48.084
- THANKS.

32:48.084 --> 32:50.208
YOU KNOW, THEY ALWAYS SAY
IT HAPPENS OVERNIGHT.

32:50.208 --> 32:51.542
- GO FOR A SWIM.

32:51.542 --> 32:53.001
TRY OUT YOUR NEW BOD.

32:53.001 --> 32:55.125
- OKAY.

32:55.125 --> 33:03.041
♪ ♪

33:07.125 --> 33:08.709
- IT'S MY FOURTH.

33:08.709 --> 33:10.042
- I DON'T CARE IF IT'S
YOUR 44TH.

33:10.042 --> 33:12.042
WE DON'T DO BUYBACKS.

33:12.042 --> 33:14.125
- I'M BROKE.
- HEY, NEWS FLASH, PRINCESS.

33:14.125 --> 33:17.417
SO IS 150%
OF THE PATRONAGE HERE.

33:18.876 --> 33:20.292
- OH, THERE SHE IS.
WELCOME BACK.

33:20.292 --> 33:21.917
HOW WAS YOUR VACAY?

33:21.917 --> 33:23.917
- OH, I WENT SURFING,
GOT HIT BY A JET SKI,

33:23.917 --> 33:25.876
SAW A DOLPHIN MASTURBATE.
- YEAH?

33:25.876 --> 33:28.250
WELL, MY FINGER'S BROKEN,
MY PARENTS ARE DIVORCED,

33:28.250 --> 33:30.750
AND MY DAD'S A FAIRY, SO--
- A FAIRY?

33:30.750 --> 33:32.166
HELLO, 1983.

33:32.166 --> 33:34.041
DID YOU GET
MY CO2 TANKS?

33:34.041 --> 33:35.667
- YEAH. HEY, CAN YOU
MAKE IT QUICK?

33:35.667 --> 33:36.876
I GOTTA GET OUT OF HERE.

33:36.876 --> 33:39.792
- YEAH, YEAH.
- THANK YOU.

33:39.792 --> 33:41.250
HEY.

33:41.250 --> 33:44.792
YOU KNOW, NOT FOR NOTHIN',
BUT, UH,

33:44.792 --> 33:47.292
NO ONE LIKES TO HEAR
A GROWN MAN WHINE.

33:47.292 --> 33:50.375
IT'S LIKE THE VERBAL EQUIVALENT
OF A DUDE WEARING UGGS.

33:50.375 --> 33:52.292
- YEAH, WELL, I APPRECIATE
THE SYMPATHY, THANKS.

33:52.292 --> 33:53.709
- GET OVER IT.

33:53.709 --> 33:55.333
FIONA DOESN'T
HAVE ROOM FOR IT.

33:55.333 --> 33:56.584
SHE'S BUSTING HER ASS
JUST TO KEEP FOOD ON THE TABLE.

33:56.584 --> 33:58.125
- GOOD DENIZENS
OF COOK COUNTY,

33:58.125 --> 34:00.042
I HAVE A PROPOSITION.

34:00.042 --> 34:02.000
[all murmuring]

34:02.000 --> 34:03.458
DO YOU REMEMBER--

34:03.458 --> 34:05.250
DO YOU REMEMBER
THE HOLDUP

34:05.250 --> 34:08.750
OF THAT JEWELRY STORE
ON SOUTH ASHLAND IN '92?

34:08.750 --> 34:10.041
- OH, YEAH, SURE.

34:10.041 --> 34:11.709
- BASTARDS CLEANED OUT
THESE POOR SPICS

34:11.709 --> 34:13.709
OF EVERY PIECE OF CRAP
THAT THEY HAD.

34:13.709 --> 34:14.917
THAT WAS MY MOTHER.

34:14.917 --> 34:16.208
SHE DID THE HEIST.

34:16.208 --> 34:19.876
AND I THINK SHE BURIED THE CRAP
IN MY BACKYARD.

34:19.876 --> 34:21.168
- HOW DO YOU KNOW THAT?

34:21.168 --> 34:22.667
- WELL, SHE STASHED IT
SOMEWHERE

34:22.667 --> 34:24.750
AND THEN
SHE FORGOT WHERE.

34:24.750 --> 34:27.667
SO THE OTHER DAY
I WAS PLANTING SOME BASIL.

34:27.667 --> 34:29.750
I'VE RECENTLY GOTTEN
BACK INTO GARDENING.

34:29.750 --> 34:32.542
AND I FOUND THIS.

34:32.542 --> 34:34.375
- SHIT, IS THAT GOLD?

34:34.375 --> 34:35.876
- COULD BE.

34:35.876 --> 34:37.041
PRETTY DIRTY,
GOTTA GET IT APPRAISED.

34:37.041 --> 34:39.667
THE POINT BEING,
THIS IS ONLY THE TIP

34:39.667 --> 34:41.041
OF THE GOLDEN ICEBERG.

34:41.041 --> 34:43.959
NOW I CAN'T DIG IT
ALL UP BY MYSELF.

34:43.959 --> 34:46.792
SO I WILL GIVE
A SIZEABLE CUT

34:46.792 --> 34:49.458
TO ANYONE WHO HELPS ME
UNEARTH IT.

34:49.458 --> 34:50.917
SO WHO'S WITH ME?

34:50.917 --> 34:53.125
[sparse chuckles]

34:55.083 --> 34:57.166
- FUCK IT. WHY NOT?
- I'M IN.

34:57.166 --> 34:59.876
- THERE YOU GO.
BRAVO, SOLDIERS.

34:59.876 --> 35:01.876
ONWARD, ONWARD.
LET'S GO.

35:01.876 --> 35:03.542
- LET'S DO IT.
- THAT'S THE SPIRIT.

35:03.542 --> 35:06.042
THIS IS WHAT
MADE AMERICA GREAT.

35:20.083 --> 35:24.041
- EW, PERIOD! PERIOD!

35:24.041 --> 35:28.542
[laughter]

35:39.917 --> 35:42.917
- HEY. WHAT'D I MISS
AT THE POOL?

35:46.250 --> 35:49.250
- [cooing]

35:54.667 --> 35:56.584
- SHOULD WE--
- LET'S JUST MAKE SURE

35:56.584 --> 35:58.584
WE EXPLORED
ALL OTHER OPTIONS.

35:58.584 --> 36:00.584
- OKAY.

36:00.584 --> 36:02.792
WHAT ABOUT THAT MAID
YOU USED TO WORK WITH?

36:02.792 --> 36:05.000
- CHANTRELLE?
TOO CRAZY.

36:05.000 --> 36:07.250
- HOW ABOUT MACIE
DOWN AT THE OLD FOLKS HOME?

36:07.250 --> 36:08.917
- TOO MEDICATED.
- FIONA?

36:08.917 --> 36:11.292
- TOO WHITE.

36:11.292 --> 36:13.208
- REALLY?
IS THAT A CONCERN OF YOURS?

36:13.208 --> 36:15.709
- I WANT IT TO HAVE
MY GENETIC MATERIAL,

36:15.709 --> 36:17.208
OR AT LEAST
LOOK LIKE IT DOES.

36:17.208 --> 36:18.959
- WHAT ABOUT
YOUR COUSIN SHARONDA?

36:18.959 --> 36:20.333
- I CALLED HER THIS MORNING.

36:20.333 --> 36:22.834
SHE FELL OFF THE WAGON,
WAS FRIED BY NOON.

36:22.834 --> 36:24.750
- WELL, WHAT ABOUT
YOUR OTHER COUSIN?

36:24.750 --> 36:26.000
YOU KNOW, THE, UH,
PRETTY ONE?

36:26.000 --> 36:28.084
- OH, THE PRETTY ONE?

36:28.084 --> 36:30.208
- NO, 'CAUSE I WANT OUR KID
TO LOOK PRETTY LIKE YOU.

36:30.208 --> 36:32.959
I MEAN--
- SHE'S 13.

36:32.959 --> 36:34.458
- WOW.

36:34.458 --> 36:37.042
SHE SEEMS OLDER.

36:37.042 --> 36:39.208
[broom sweeping]

36:43.458 --> 36:45.500
- [grunts]

36:45.500 --> 36:48.126
- AAH.
[grunts]

36:48.126 --> 36:50.500
MOTHER OF CHRIST,
IT STINKS.

36:50.500 --> 36:52.750
THERE'S SO MUCH SHIT
IN THE YARD.

36:52.750 --> 36:54.458
- SHUT UP
AND KEEP DIGGING.

36:54.458 --> 36:56.750
THE ONE ARM WONDER'S
MAKING MORE PROGRESS THAN YOU.

36:56.750 --> 36:59.168
- THIS IS AS FAR
AS YOU GOT?

36:59.168 --> 37:01.876
- DON'T JUDGE!

37:01.876 --> 37:04.876
- FRANK, DO YOU KNOW
FOR CERTAIN

37:04.876 --> 37:07.209
THERE'S JEWELRY
BURIED OUT HERE?

37:07.209 --> 37:10.042
- UH, YOU KNOW WHAT?

37:10.042 --> 37:11.792
TRY ALONG
THAT FENCE THERE.

37:11.792 --> 37:15.083
I SAW HER ROOTIN' AROUND
IN THERE LIKE A BADGER.

37:16.917 --> 37:18.333
- WOWEE.

37:18.333 --> 37:20.292
IS IT DESERT STORM NIGHT
AT THE CHEESECAKE FACTORY?

37:20.292 --> 37:22.709
- WHY ARE YOU
ACTING LIKE A DICK TO MANDY?

37:22.709 --> 37:24.333
- I THINK THAT
QUALIFIES AS

37:24.333 --> 37:26.168
NONE OF YOUR FUCKIN'
BUSINESS.

37:26.168 --> 37:27.709
- WELL, SHE CALLED ME
FROM AUNT'S HOUSE,

37:27.709 --> 37:29.208
SAID YOU TOLD HER
TO GO HOME.

37:29.208 --> 37:30.709
- IS MOLLY LEAVING TOO?

37:30.709 --> 37:32.083
- WHAT? NO, DEBS.
LOOK, MAN.

37:32.083 --> 37:35.126
SHE IS ALWAYS ON ME
ABOUT, YOU KNOW,

37:35.126 --> 37:37.750
OUR  PLANS FOR THE NIGHT
AND WHEN

37:37.750 --> 37:39.292
WE'RE  GOING TO SEE
HER FRIEND'S BAND

37:39.292 --> 37:40.750
AND WHAT WE'RE  DOING
NEXT WEEK.

37:40.750 --> 37:42.168
- SO SHE LIKES
HANGING OUT WITH YOU.

37:42.168 --> 37:44.084
THAT'S NOT A CRIME.
- I LIKE MOLLY.

37:44.084 --> 37:45.876
- SHE'S NOT MY WIFE.

37:45.876 --> 37:48.542
- NO, SHE'S A GOOD PERSON
WHO DOES NICE THINGS FOR YOU.

37:48.542 --> 37:50.084
- WHAT ARE YOU,
HER FUCKIN' LAWYER?

37:50.084 --> 37:51.750
- NO, I'M HER BEST FRIEND.

37:51.750 --> 37:53.458
ALL RIGHT, AND YOU'RE ACTING
LIKE A DOUCHE BAG.

37:53.458 --> 37:55.250
YOU WANT OUT? END IT.
YOU DON'T?

37:55.250 --> 37:56.959
STOP TREATING HER
LIKE GARBAGE.

37:56.959 --> 37:58.458
BUT JUST 'CAUSE KAREN
WIPED HER ASS WITH YOU

37:58.458 --> 38:01.375
DOESN'T GIVE YOU THE RIGHT
TO SHIT ON MANDY.

38:01.375 --> 38:03.000
[door opens]

38:03.000 --> 38:05.584
- GUYS, BAD NEWS.
WE ALL GOTTA DIG TONIGHT.

38:05.584 --> 38:08.000
THE CITY'S COMING AND
FRANK CAN'T FIND AUNT GINGER.

38:08.000 --> 38:10.042
- SO?

38:10.042 --> 38:11.250
- SO SOMEONE'S GOING TO JAIL
IF WE DON'T FIND HER.

38:11.250 --> 38:12.917
- YEAH, FRANK, YOU MEAN.

38:12.917 --> 38:14.000
- THERE'S A BODY.
WE KNOW ABOUT IT.

38:14.000 --> 38:15.876
WE'RE ACCOMPLICES.

38:15.876 --> 38:17.083
- ONCE AGAIN SADDLED
WITH A MESS WE DIDN'T CREATE.

38:17.083 --> 38:18.458
- SOONER WE GET OUT THERE
AND DIG,

38:18.458 --> 38:20.209
THE SOONER IT'LL ALL
BE OVER.

38:20.209 --> 38:22.625
- I STILL GOT BLISTERS
ON MY HAND FROM YESTERDAY.

38:22.625 --> 38:24.168
- I CAN DIG.

38:24.168 --> 38:27.042
I HAVE PRETTY DEVELOPED
UPPER ARMS FOR A CHICK.

38:30.126 --> 38:31.417
- I NEED TO BORROW
YOUR TURKEY BASTER.

38:31.417 --> 38:34.208
- I DON'T WANT MOLLY
TO LEAVE!

38:34.208 --> 38:35.667
- WHAT'S WITH HER?

38:35.667 --> 38:38.333
- SHE GOT HER PERIOD
AT THE POOL TODAY.

38:38.333 --> 38:40.292
- I CAN'T WAIT
TO GET MY PERIOD.

38:40.292 --> 38:44.292
MOM SAID IT'S THE BODY'S
TRIBUTE TO FEMALE SACRIFICE.

38:50.500 --> 38:51.750
- YOU'RE NOT A GIRL,
HONEY.

38:51.750 --> 38:53.000
YOU'RE A BOY
WHO WAS RAISED

38:53.000 --> 38:55.126
BY A JACKED-UP METH HEAD
OF A MOM,

38:55.126 --> 38:57.168
WHO MADE YOU
THINK YOU WERE A GIRL

38:57.168 --> 39:00.333
BECAUSE SHE HATES MEN.

39:00.333 --> 39:02.625
- I'M NOT A GIRL?

39:02.625 --> 39:04.625
- LIP.

39:09.500 --> 39:11.792
- [crying]

39:11.792 --> 39:13.625
[knock at door]
- DEBBIE?

39:13.625 --> 39:16.126
- [sobs]
IT WASN'T REAL.

39:16.126 --> 39:17.667
IT WAS KETCHUP.

39:17.667 --> 39:20.292
THEY DID IT
IN FRONT OF EVERYONE!

39:20.292 --> 39:24.209
- WHO?
- THE GIRLS AT THE POOL.

39:24.209 --> 39:27.041
- DEBS.
- [crying]

39:27.041 --> 39:29.917
THEY'RE PRETTY AND
BOYS NOTICE THEM.

39:29.917 --> 39:32.168
- WELL, THEY WON'T
BE PRETTY FOR LONG.

39:32.168 --> 39:33.834
THEY'RE GONNA MAKE
ALL THE BAD DECISIONS

39:33.834 --> 39:36.709
AND YOU'RE GONNA GET TO LEARN
FROM THEIR MISTAKES.

39:38.292 --> 39:40.876
- WHY DO THEY
HAVE TO BE SO MEAN?

39:43.042 --> 39:45.292
- SOME GIRLS
ARE JUST JERKS.

39:45.292 --> 39:48.709
LIKE THAT CHICK
AT THE STORE YESTERDAY.

39:48.709 --> 39:50.876
DID I DESERVE THAT?
NO.

39:50.876 --> 39:53.292
BUT DID I TAKE HER SHIT?
NO WAY.

39:53.292 --> 39:56.000
'CAUSE I'M BETTER
THAN THAT AND SO ARE YOU.

39:56.000 --> 39:58.333
NOBODY FUCKS
WITH THE GALLAGHERS.

39:58.333 --> 40:01.126
- [crying]

40:03.041 --> 40:05.917
- DEBBIE?

40:05.917 --> 40:07.876
- GO AWAY.

40:10.500 --> 40:11.959
- OPEN THE DOOR.

40:11.959 --> 40:13.959
- [deep breath]

40:22.125 --> 40:25.083
[crying]

40:30.001 --> 40:31.250
- COME ON.

40:31.250 --> 40:33.001
- [sobs]

40:33.001 --> 40:35.001
- WE GOTTA DIG.

40:53.625 --> 40:56.625
[rock music]

40:56.625 --> 40:59.709
♪ ♪

40:59.709 --> 41:02.750
- [gasps]

41:02.750 --> 41:05.083
OH! OH!

41:09.126 --> 41:12.168
I THOUGHT YOU TOOK
A VOW OF SILENCE.

41:12.168 --> 41:15.001
THE SILENCE DOESN'T INCLUDE
THE INTERNET?

41:15.001 --> 41:18.125
♪ ♪

41:18.125 --> 41:22.168
YOU HAVE BEEN BLOGGING
ABOUT ME EVERY DAY?

41:22.168 --> 41:24.041
- [grunts]

41:24.041 --> 41:25.792
- I THINK I'M GONNA PUKE.

41:25.792 --> 41:28.542
- MUSCLE THROUGH IT.
WE GOTTA FIND HER.

41:28.542 --> 41:29.876
WHERE'D CARL GO?

41:29.876 --> 41:31.292
- HUH?

41:31.292 --> 41:34.876
- NINJA!
- CARL! NO!

41:34.876 --> 41:36.333
- NO!

41:36.333 --> 41:38.209
[explosion]
- AAH!

41:38.209 --> 41:40.041
- OH, MY GOD.
- SHIT, CARL!

41:40.041 --> 41:41.375
[car alarm blaring]

41:41.375 --> 41:42.876
THAT ACTUALLY KINDA WORKED.

41:42.876 --> 41:44.333
- YOU GET THOSE
FROM THE FIREWORKS STASH?

41:44.333 --> 41:46.168
- YEAH.
- GO GET SOME MORE.

41:46.168 --> 41:48.292
- IAN?

41:48.292 --> 41:51.625
- REEKS OUT HERE.

41:51.625 --> 41:53.542
HEY, LISTEN.

41:53.542 --> 41:56.000
OH, MAN.

41:56.000 --> 41:58.208
ABOUT ALL THE STUFF,
JUST WITH MY DAD, I--

41:58.208 --> 42:01.834
- OH, MY GOD, WHY ARE WE
STILL TALKING ABOUT THIS?

42:01.834 --> 42:03.750
I MEAN, REALLY?
CHRIST.

42:03.750 --> 42:06.876
- OKAY, SO, LIKE,
WHENEVER YOU NEED ME

42:06.876 --> 42:08.667
I'M, LIKE, THERE FOR YOU,
BUT THE ONE TIME I NEED YOU,

42:08.667 --> 42:11.667
YOU'RE LIKE, "SCREW OFF"?

42:14.208 --> 42:17.333
- CARL THINKS
HE'S A CANCER SURVIVOR.

42:17.333 --> 42:21.125
MOLLY THINKS SHE'S A GIRL
WITH A PENIS.

42:21.125 --> 42:24.667
DEBBIE'S GETTING TERRORIZED
AT THE PUBLIC POOL.

42:24.667 --> 42:27.126
THIS YARD SMELLS LIKE
A SEWER.

42:27.126 --> 42:29.041
I GOT THREE DRUNK ASSHOLES

42:29.041 --> 42:31.084
OPERATING POWER TOOLS
BEHIND ME.

42:31.084 --> 42:33.001
AND THE BITCHES AT WORK

42:33.001 --> 42:35.168
LOCKED ME
IN A BATHROOM TODAY.

42:35.168 --> 42:36.709
OH!

42:36.709 --> 42:40.542
AND WE MIGHT ALL BE ON THE VERGE
OF GOING TO PRISON.

42:40.542 --> 42:44.375
SO YOU WANNA TALK?
FINE.

42:44.375 --> 42:45.917
GRAB A SHOVEL.

42:45.917 --> 42:48.458
TALK YOUR FACE OFF
ABOUT HOW YOUR DAD

42:48.458 --> 42:50.375
GAVE A BLOWJOB
TO A TEENAGER,

42:50.375 --> 42:52.042
BUT DIG WHILE YOU DO IT.

42:52.042 --> 42:53.166
- YOU KNOW WHAT?

42:53.166 --> 42:55.375
I'M REALLY TIRED
OF PLAYING THIS

42:55.375 --> 42:58.084
"MY TRAGEDY IS BIGGER
THAN YOUR TRAGEDY" GAME.

42:58.084 --> 43:00.000
MY ENTIRE WORLD
GOT ROCKED,

43:00.000 --> 43:02.250
AND IT'S, LIKE,
NOT EVEN ON YOUR RADAR.

43:02.250 --> 43:05.042
WE'RE IN A RELATIONSHIP!

43:05.042 --> 43:08.750
WHAT'S IMPORTANT TO ME
SHOULD BE IMPORTANT TO YOU.

43:08.750 --> 43:10.709
- LOOK AT US.

43:10.709 --> 43:14.876
WE ARE LITERALLY
DIGGING UP A BODY.

43:14.876 --> 43:17.709
HOW DO YOU EVEN
COMPARE OUR SITUATIONS?

43:24.959 --> 43:27.250
[chuckles]
OH, THAT'S GREAT.

43:27.250 --> 43:30.041
WALK AWAY.

43:30.041 --> 43:33.876
THAT'S A REAL PUSSY MOVE.

43:33.876 --> 43:37.209
YEAH, WHY DON'T YOU GO CRY
TO YOUR GAY DAD ABOUT IT?

43:41.084 --> 43:42.876
- SO I'LL JUST
BE CARRYING IT

43:42.876 --> 43:44.917
AND YOU TWO TAKE IT FROM ME
WHEN IT COMES OUT?

43:44.917 --> 43:46.333
- YES, MAMA.
- 'CAUSE LORD KNOWS

43:46.333 --> 43:48.584
I AM TOO OLD TO BE
RAISING AN INFANT.

43:48.584 --> 43:50.084
- IT WILL BE OUR CHILD.

43:50.084 --> 43:51.333
IT WILL BE YOUR GRANDCHILD.

43:51.333 --> 43:54.083
- AW, YOU WERE
SUCH A SWEET BABY.

43:54.083 --> 43:57.417
BUT LORD,
WERE YOU A TERRIBLE EATER.

43:57.417 --> 43:59.000
[chuckles]

43:59.000 --> 44:01.208
IT'D GET ALL UP IN YOUR HAIR
AND IN YOUR NOSE--

44:01.208 --> 44:03.000
- EVERYTHING OKAY?

44:03.000 --> 44:05.250
- YEAH, JUST A SECOND.

44:05.250 --> 44:08.208
OH, THIS COMES
THE TRICKY PART.

44:08.208 --> 44:10.417
[slapping]

44:10.417 --> 44:13.876
[groans]

44:16.458 --> 44:18.208
- NOT MUCH IN THERE.

44:18.208 --> 44:19.876
WE COULD'VE USED
AN EYEDROPPER.

44:19.876 --> 44:21.542
JEEZ, KEVIN.

44:21.542 --> 44:25.168
- [exhales]
- OKAY.

44:25.168 --> 44:29.458
- [deep breaths]

44:29.458 --> 44:32.500
BOTTOMS UP.

44:38.917 --> 44:40.709
- OOH.

44:40.709 --> 44:43.001
WARMER THAN I EXPECTED.

44:43.001 --> 44:45.333
OOH. [laughs]

44:51.168 --> 44:53.250
- OKAY, BEDTIME, GANG.

44:53.250 --> 44:55.917
WE'LL START AGAIN
IN THE MORNING.

44:55.917 --> 44:57.917
- FUCK.

45:00.041 --> 45:02.209
[lighter clicks]

45:04.876 --> 45:06.834
DON'T WORRY
ABOUT YOUR DWEEB.

45:06.834 --> 45:09.876
HE'S JUST OFF
LICKING HIS WOUNDS.

45:09.876 --> 45:13.292
HE'LL BE BACK.

45:13.292 --> 45:16.333
- WE GALLAGHERS SURE KNOW
HOW TO PICK 'EM, HUH?

45:18.667 --> 45:20.667
SEE YOU IN THE MORNING.

45:25.041 --> 45:29.084
[dialing]

45:29.084 --> 45:30.917
[phone line trilling]

45:30.917 --> 45:32.834
[voicemail beeps]

45:32.834 --> 45:35.709
- HEY, KAREN.
IT'S LIP.

45:35.709 --> 45:39.250
UM, JUST WANTED
TO GIVE YOU AN UPDATE--

45:39.250 --> 45:40.750
WHEREVER THE FUCK YOU ARE.

45:40.750 --> 45:45.168
UM, YOUR KID,
HE'S DOING GREAT.

45:45.168 --> 45:49.542
UM, YOUR MOM AND
EX-HUSBAND, THEY'RE--

45:49.542 --> 45:52.126
THEY'RE ALSO DOING GREAT.

45:52.126 --> 45:55.792
MY DAD,
WHO YOU FUCKED,

45:55.792 --> 46:00.500
HE'S DOING GREAT.
AND, UM--

46:00.500 --> 46:06.250
I'M DOING REALLY,
REALLY GREAT--

46:06.250 --> 46:10.292
JUST IN CASE
YOU WERE WONDERING.

46:10.292 --> 46:14.959
YOU SELFISH, IGNORANT,
HEINOUS PIECE OF DOGSHIT.

46:14.959 --> 46:17.168
THANK YOU FOR LEAVING
AND NEVER COMING BACK.

46:17.168 --> 46:22.208
YOU--WE ALL OWE YOU
A HUGE FUCKING FAVOR!

46:25.168 --> 46:28.168
YOU ROCK.

46:36.834 --> 46:40.458
HI.
GO INSIDE?

46:40.458 --> 46:43.250
BRING THAT WITH YOU.

46:43.250 --> 46:45.083
COME ON.

46:45.083 --> 46:47.168
[sighs]

46:54.333 --> 46:56.917
- [sighs]

47:02.041 --> 47:04.001
[chuckles]

47:07.041 --> 47:08.667
HEY, IT'S ME.

47:08.667 --> 47:12.166
UH, JUST WONDERING
WHERE YOU ARE.

47:12.166 --> 47:16.208
CALL, TEXT, WHATEVS.
BYE.

47:20.125 --> 47:22.333
[sighs]

47:33.458 --> 47:35.126
- I MEAN, NO WONDER
SHE FLIPPED OUT.

47:35.126 --> 47:38.126
I MEAN, SHE'S GOT
SO MUCH ON HER PLATE.

47:38.126 --> 47:40.250
SHE NEEDS ME THERE FOR HER.

47:40.250 --> 47:43.959
I--YOU KNOW, I GOTTA
WORK ON MY STUFF TOO.

47:43.959 --> 47:46.208
- SI.  SO HARD FOR YOU.

47:46.208 --> 47:49.333
POOR STEVIE.

47:49.333 --> 47:52.126
YOU READY TO GO AGAIN?

47:52.126 --> 47:54.041
- YEAH.

47:54.041 --> 47:56.542
- [giggles]

47:56.542 --> 47:59.333
[both moaning]

47:59.333 --> 48:00.917
- FUCK.

48:00.917 --> 48:06.166
[metal clanking]

48:08.084 --> 48:10.250
- I'M A DICK!

48:10.250 --> 48:12.250
MANDY?

48:14.208 --> 48:16.375
I'M A DICK.

48:16.375 --> 48:19.375
CAN YOU COME DOWN?

48:19.375 --> 48:22.042
[dog barks]

48:31.042 --> 48:33.083
HEY.

48:33.083 --> 48:35.709
- I'M NOT A TOOL.

48:38.750 --> 48:40.208
- YEAH, I KNOW.

48:40.208 --> 48:44.750
- SO YOU DON'T GET
TO TREAT ME LIKE ONE.

48:44.750 --> 48:48.750
- I KNOW.

48:48.750 --> 48:51.125
COME DOWN.

48:54.667 --> 48:56.542
PLEASE?

49:02.917 --> 49:05.917
[rock music]

49:05.917 --> 49:13.917
♪ ♪

49:19.209 --> 49:21.667
[fireworks squealing]

49:55.125 --> 49:57.417
- HEY. WHOA.
GUYS, GUYS.

49:57.417 --> 49:59.083
NO FUCKING GUNS,
ALL RIGHT?

49:59.083 --> 50:02.126
IT'S JUST A DRUNK
OLD LADY IN THERE.

50:02.126 --> 50:05.083
- COME ON.
COME ON.

50:05.083 --> 50:07.500
- FUCK.

50:30.041 --> 50:32.250
- [coughs]

50:38.917 --> 50:40.168
WHERE'S DEBBIE?

50:40.168 --> 50:42.083
- SHE'S AT THE POOL.

50:42.083 --> 50:44.126
- WE GOTTA KEEP DIGGING.

50:44.126 --> 50:45.500
- [cooing]

50:45.500 --> 50:48.500
[rock music]

50:48.500 --> 50:56.500
♪ ♪

50:58.584 --> 51:02.292
[clock chiming]

51:02.292 --> 51:05.959
♪ ♪

51:05.959 --> 51:07.292
- [grunts]

51:07.292 --> 51:08.917
- OH, COME ON.

51:08.917 --> 51:12.084
[clock chimes]

51:12.084 --> 51:13.250
- OH, FUCK.

51:13.250 --> 51:14.959
- JESUS CHRIST.
- HEY!

51:14.959 --> 51:16.959
FUCKERS!

51:16.959 --> 51:18.458
- OH, FUCK.

51:18.458 --> 51:21.209
- AAH!
- FUCK.

51:21.209 --> 51:22.250
- GO!
- FUCKERS!

51:22.250 --> 51:23.333
[gunshot]

51:23.333 --> 51:25.250
- FUCK!
- FUCK!

51:25.250 --> 51:27.126
- FUCKING--
[gunshot]

51:27.126 --> 51:28.792
- NO FUCKING WAY!

51:28.792 --> 51:30.584
- FUCK!
FUCKING NED!

51:30.584 --> 51:32.792
ARE YOU FUCKING HIM TOO?

51:32.792 --> 51:34.041
- AAH!
FUCKING DRIVE.

51:34.041 --> 51:36.001
- YOU GOT SHOT,
MICKEY!

51:36.001 --> 51:38.750
- YES, I FUCKING KNOW
I GOT SHOT.

51:38.750 --> 51:41.084
[tires screeching]

51:41.084 --> 51:43.084
[gunshot]

51:45.417 --> 51:46.834
- [grunts]

51:46.834 --> 51:54.375
♪ ♪

51:54.375 --> 51:57.292
- REMEMBER,
DO NOT SIT ON CUSHIONS,

51:57.292 --> 51:59.292
CARPETS, ANYTHING FOAM,
OR POROUS.

51:59.292 --> 52:01.709
SAY THEIR NAMES SLOWLY
AND CALMLY.

52:01.709 --> 52:03.125
IF YOU FEEL SOMETHING
CRAWLING ON YOU

52:03.125 --> 52:05.834
DON'T SCREAM, JUST SHAKE
THE BODY PART LIGHTLY.

52:05.834 --> 52:07.834
OKAY?
LET'S DO THIS.

52:09.041 --> 52:12.041
[tires screeching]

52:12.041 --> 52:13.876
- COME ON.
- HOLY SHIT.

52:13.876 --> 52:14.876
HOLY SHIT.
- FUCK.

52:14.876 --> 52:16.542
- [groans]

52:16.542 --> 52:20.001
- FUCK.

52:20.001 --> 52:22.084
[tires screeching]

52:33.084 --> 52:34.792
- I'M JUST GONNA
TAKE ANOTHER MINUTE.

52:34.792 --> 52:36.876
- TAKE YOUR TIME.

52:36.876 --> 52:38.667
- YOU KIDDING ME?
- STAY THERE.

52:38.667 --> 52:40.041
- AAH!
- OH, JESUS.

52:40.041 --> 52:42.083
- JUST ONE FUCKING
OLD LADY, HUH?

52:42.083 --> 52:43.166
AAH! OW! OW.

52:43.166 --> 52:45.709
[children crying]

52:45.709 --> 52:47.041
- WELL, IF IT ISN'T
THE TOUGHEST BADASS

52:47.041 --> 52:49.458
FAG BEATER THIS SIDE
OF THE CHICAGO RIVER.

52:49.458 --> 52:52.375
- FUCK OFF.

52:52.375 --> 52:56.292
- [grunts]

52:56.292 --> 53:02.458
♪ ♪

53:02.458 --> 53:04.250
- I'LL SHOW YOU SOME TITS.

53:10.083 --> 53:11.625
[deep breath]

53:17.042 --> 53:25.084
♪ ♪

53:34.584 --> 53:36.166
[chuckles]

53:38.458 --> 53:42.667
- [screams, grunts]

53:42.667 --> 53:46.792
♪ ♪

53:46.792 --> 53:49.667
[knock at door]

53:49.667 --> 53:51.209
- FIONA'S FITS BETTER,
DOESN'T IT?

53:51.209 --> 53:52.500
- SURE.

53:52.500 --> 53:58.292
♪ ♪

53:58.292 --> 54:01.000
[children crying]

54:01.000 --> 54:03.625
- [screaming]

54:03.625 --> 54:05.625
- OH, MY.

54:05.625 --> 54:07.125
- YOU'RE ALMOST DONE,
MICKEY.

54:07.125 --> 54:09.042
- AAH!

54:09.042 --> 54:10.959
- [grunts]

54:15.084 --> 54:16.417
HA!

54:16.417 --> 54:19.168
[giggles]

54:19.168 --> 54:21.458
[squeals]

54:22.667 --> 54:26.168
- [screaming, groaning]

54:27.208 --> 54:29.125
- IAN, WHAT THE FUCK?

54:29.125 --> 54:31.001
- I CAN EXPLAIN THIS.

54:31.001 --> 54:33.792
- WHO THE HELL ARE YOU?

54:33.792 --> 54:37.792
- I'M BRITNEY STURGES
FROM CHILD PROTECTIVE SERVICES.

54:40.001 --> 54:42.250
- SHE JUST WALKED IN.

54:44.500 --> 54:46.292
- YES!

54:46.292 --> 54:48.126
OH, MY GOD.

54:48.126 --> 54:50.041
I TOTALLY ALMOST DROWNED
A SLUT!

54:50.041 --> 54:51.709
SHE WAS KICKING
AND SCRATCHING,

54:51.709 --> 54:53.959
BUT I HELD MY BREATH
AND HUNG ON

54:53.959 --> 54:55.458
UNTIL SHE PASSED OUT!

54:55.458 --> 54:57.166
OH, MY GOD.
GUESS WHAT.

54:57.166 --> 55:01.084
YOU DO NOT "F"
WITH DEBBIE GALLAGHER!

55:01.084 --> 55:02.584
[chuckles]
DON'T "F" WITH ME.

55:02.584 --> 55:04.001
- DEBS.

55:04.001 --> 55:05.417
- YEAH. WHAT?

55:05.417 --> 55:07.084
[chuckles]

55:07.084 --> 55:10.208
[baby crying]
